imdb.plot outline: Emmy-Nominated lifestyle show, Northeast Living brings viewers on a life-style trip through New England (and occasionally overseas). Join host Mar Jennings and correspondent Elaine Irvin as they travel New England - visiting landmarks, "shops around the corner", and those places you never really knew existed. Along the way you'll even get some great tips from Mar as he helps to improve your life both physically and emotionally.
